com.vmware.nsx.node

Class NodeFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.node.NodeFactory

  • public class NodeFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    NodeFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.node package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
